---
name: summarize
description: Summarize text content concisely
author: blogus
category: writing
tags:
  - summary
  - content
  - text
model:
  id: gpt-4o-mini
  temperature: 0.5
  max_tokens: 500
goal: Create clear, accurate summaries
variables:
  - name: content
    description: The content to summarize
    required: true
  - name: length
    description: Desired summary length
    required: false
    default: "2-3 paragraphs"
    enum:
      - "1 sentence"
      - "1 paragraph"
      - "2-3 paragraphs"
      - "bullet points"
---

Summarize the following content in {{length}}.

## Content
{{content}}

## Guidelines
- Capture the main ideas and key points
- Maintain accuracy - don't add information not present
- Use clear, concise language
- Preserve the original tone when appropriate
